Package: bayesact
Type: Package
Title: The Bayesian Actuarial Package
Version: 0.0.8
Author: Chris Waller, Zongwen Tan
Maintainer: Chris Waller <chriswaller26@gmail.com>, Zongwen Tan <tzw0423@hotmail.com>
Description: This package has been developed to create simple functions for 
    running linear and non-linear Bayesian models that utilise the BRMS 
    package to build actuarial models, e.g. multivariate frequency-severity 
    models with censoring at the deductible.
License: None
Encoding: UTF-8
